865,IssueCommentEvent,2017-08-01 20:50:00+00:00,74008159,ickc/pantable,34238,reenberg,,,246957716,319492711,"@ickc, I see your point of the reversability of pantable and pantable2csv.  I just thought that the reverse was a pure gimmick or at least I didn't see any practical use cases for it as a filter.  

