1697,IssueCommentEvent,2018-07-23 17:19:47+00:00,27283062,ktbyers/netmiko,899716,ktbyers,,,343129804,407134807,"@RamVic A more common pattern would probably be something similar to the following (i.e. to use a for-loop and loop over the IP addresses):

