1712,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-02 20:29:30+00:00,27283062,ktbyers/netmiko,899716,ktbyers,,,309094797,378034587,"So what it is showing is that you keep hitting enter and are not getting any response back. Is this device super slow?

Maybe try setting a global_delay_factor of 4 in ConnectHandler?

You could also maybe try setting the default_enter to '\r\n' in case that is messing up the terminal server, console connection in some way.

```
net_connect = ConnectHandler(
    device_type='generic_termserver_telnet',        # changed
    ip='127.0.0.1',
    username='pyclass',
    password='cisco',
    global_delay_factor=4,
    default_enter='\r\n',
    port=5000)
```",{},OWNER,User,False
