3349,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-22 09:44:55+00:00,55278637,Grk0/python-libconf,9025497,Grk0,,,265382419,338464761,"@ssweeny: Thanks a lot for you interest in python-libconf and for your patch. What problem is it designed to solve?

