4600,IssueCommentEvent,2017-06-07 16:55:33+00:00,66664935,odrling/peony-twitter,21046116,odrling,,,234102640,306857385,"Peony should relies on error codes to raise a corresponding exception, if it couldn't find the error code then it will raise an exception corresponding to the HTTP status of the response, if no exception was found for the status code it should raise a `PeonyException` (and I hope somebody would open an issue for this)

