5536,IssueCommentEvent,2016-08-30 16:03:31+00:00,58303578,Ezibenroc/PyRoaringBitMap,391987,lemire,,,172954122,243490522,"With my PR, here are the results for this script

```python
import timeit
setup=""from array import array; import pyroaring; import ctypes; t = [i for i in range(1000000)];""
print(timeit.timeit(stmt='x=pyroaring.BitMap(t)',setup=setup,number=100))
