7968,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-18 20:42:04+00:00,24774658,boto/boto3,1153951,massenz,327752,boto,265123891,337721601,"Thanks for the pointer to enable debug logs - it seems pretty clear, by parsing those that the waiter misses the state transition and then the Stack does not exist:
