8276,IssueCommentEvent,2015-12-28 17:59:47+00:00,38906603,uber/tchannel-python,41730,abhinav,538264,uber,123736901,167614867,"Turns out that it *is* currently possible to do this with a non-public API: `request_context` from https://github.com/uber/tchannel-python/blob/master/tchannel/context.py. We have 3 different Trace objects, though (we're working on fixing that). @junchaowu will be able to answer which one you're supposed to use with that. For the short term, this will probably suffice.

