9778,IssueCommentEvent,2017-02-07 10:18:18+00:00,3342046,RDFLib/rdflib,464192,joernhees,1401847,RDFLib,173134219,277956832,"The old method uses a dict for lookup (so O(1) per lookup), based on splits by URI parts, so (O(m) for m parts per URI). Overall O(m).

Your method goes through all namespaces (on avg. n/2), so uses O(n) for n registered namespaces.

The old method will scale better in light of many registered namespaces. Your method is likely to be faster if only few namespaces are registered.",{},,User,False
