10688,IssueCommentEvent,2017-04-19 18:55:34+00:00,30509483,clab/dynet,1481766,ccsasuke,2374376,clab,222607233,295390498,"Sorry for hijacking this thread, but just want to make sure I did not do it wrong before filing a separate issue.

