11912,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-08 01:39:03+00:00,12898486,juju/charm-tools,70613,marcoceppi,4604548,juju,256009173,327975575,"gh-pages are just static files in a branch. If you remove the master branch and create a `gh-pages` branch, set that as the primary. Then pull requests, issues, etc all work the same, but the files are published by gh in a way meant to be consumed.

