12011,IssueCommentEvent,2017-11-14 15:13:00+00:00,12407457,Exa-Networks/exabgp,2859483,switchtower,5339170,Exa-Networks,131148990,344289483,"I was able to reproduce this issue on 3.4.19
the config has 5044 routes for a specific community that we filter against:
`
cat conf_rtr.switchtower.com_ipv4.ini | grep 64512:318 -c
5044
`
 but on the router:
`
11.11.14.23     4 64512 37858694 1159621   771739    0    0    3d08h 5055
`
if I completely shutdown the process and start it back up, the number of routes are correct:
`
11.11.14.23     4 64512 37875815 1159308   771739    0    0 00:08:36 5044
`",{},NONE,User,False
