12718,IssueCommentEvent,2015-03-31 14:07:46+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,832380,bjonen,6392739,conda,64797912,88100886,"So, the source of the problem was this: The package seaborn is not available in the continuum repos in a version that is compatible with matplotlib 1.3.1. I added a binstar repository with an older version which solved my problem. 

