13045,IssueCommentEvent,2016-08-30 23:49:07+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,173803282,243617103,"> Execute P0s before any change to VMSS Create **OR VM CREATE** is merged

I get that. In the future though we should probably include the updated recordings as part of the PR so that anyone reviewing it can know that we re-ran the tests live. It's easy to forget to otherwise and the CI can't enforce it. :)

