14991,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-01 17:39:31+00:00,112676803,apple/turicreate,7563587,kwade101,10639145,apple,281900345,393955366,"One other note, although I don't know if it's relevant or not.  The first time I attempted to run Turi Create Visualization via sf.explore(), it failed to launch at all...with an error that appears to be related to an old version of Adobe Unit Types:

