thanks for the quick response. I have updated CLE and the problem was solved. However I had this second error:
```
File ""/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/claripy/backends/backend_z3.py"", line 333, in _abstract_internal
    raise ClaripyError(""unknown decl kind %d"" % decl_num)
claripy.errors.ClaripyError: unknown decl kind 2352
Segmentation fault (core dumped)
```

